Class TFMExec

All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class TFMExec
extends TFMQGItems

Concrete TFMQGItems subclass used during Transformation execution to hold execution arguments. The QGItem instances are those required (in order) to execute the transformation. In this sense these args are "outputs" from the Transformation application.
